Al Fateh University ( Arabic : جامعة الفاتح ) is the largest and most important institute of higher education in Libya . It is located in the capital Tripoli . The university was Founded in 1957 and provides undergraduate , graduate and post - graduate levels of study . It was named Al Fateh University in 1976 after the revolution of the same name . The university comprises the following faculties : Science ( the first faculty to be established ) , Engineering , Agriculture , Medicine , Pharmacy , Arts , Veterinary medicine , Dentistry , Medical Technology , Arts , Law and Economics . Another five off - campus institutions were recently incorporated into the university . 